headline: Keysight Enables AMD to Showcase Electrical PCI Express® Compliance up to 64 GT/s
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., June 18, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) announced that it helped AMD accelerate the testing of electrical compliance for PCI Express® (PCIe) specification for pre-production AMD server CPUs. By providing early access to beta software, Keysight enabled AMD to develop and test a PCI Express technology-capable server motherboard operating at up to 64 GT/s. The server was shown for the first time at the PCI-SIG Developer’s Conference June 11-12 in Santa Clara, Cal
